Package: mediascores
Title: News-sharing Ideology from Social Media Link Data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(person("Gregory", "Eady", email = "gregory.eady@gmail.com",
                  role = c("aut", "cre")),
             person("Fridolin", "Linder", role = c("aut", "ctb")))
Date: 2019-03-01
URL: https://cran.r-project.org/web/packages/mediascores/index.html
Description: Enables the examination of political communication on social media by using news stories shared on social media (via URLs) to estimate the news-sharing ideology of politicians and users, and the ideology of the content that they share.
